<% layout('/layouts/Boilerplate.ejs') %>

<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-lg-9">
      <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 rounded-4 p-4 p-md-5">
        <h1 class="fw-bold mb-4">Support</h1>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">
          We’re here to help with issues related to listings, accounts, and
          general platform use.
        </p>

        <h4 class="fw-semibold mt-4">1. Contact Support</h4>
        <p>
          If you need assistance, you can reach our support team at
          <a href="mailto:support@thebnb.com" class="text-decoration-none"
            >support@thebnb.com</a
          >.
        </p>

        <h4 class="fw-semibold mt-4">2. Common Help Topics</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Creating a new listing</li>
          <li>Editing or deleting an existing listing</li>
          <li>Image upload or image link issues</li>
          <li>Account login or access problems</li>
          <li>Reporting incorrect or inappropriate listing content</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="fw-semibold mt-4">3. Response Time</h4>
        <p>
          Our goal is to respond to support requests within 24–48 hours,
          depending on request volume and the severity of the issue.
        </p>

        <h4 class="fw-semibold mt-4">4. Reporting Problems</h4>
        <p>
          When contacting support, include as much detail as possible, such as
          the listing title, the issue you faced, screenshots if relevant, and
          the steps needed to reproduce the problem. Humans do love vague bug
          reports, but we try to resist the tradition.
        </p>

        <h4 class="fw-semibold mt-4">5. Account & Safety</h4>
        <p>
          If you believe your account has been compromised or you notice
          suspicious activity, contact support immediately so appropriate action
          can be taken.
        </p>

        <h4 class="fw-semibold mt-4">6. Feedback</h4>
        <p class="mb-0">
          We also welcome suggestions for improving The BNB. If you have feature
          ideas or usability feedback, send them to
          <a href="mailto:feedback@thebnb.com" class="text-decoration-none"
            >feedback@thebnb.com</a
          >.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
